        <text><![CDATA[<p>This resolution supports the designation of National FFA (Future Farmers of America) Week.</p><p>It also celebrates the 50th anniversary of the chartering of Alaska as a State FFA Association of the National FFA Organization.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
